Install the prereqs
-------------------

apt-get install puppet virtualbox virtualbox-ose dkms linux-headers-$(uname -r)
gem install veewee vagrant

Building a buddycloud dev vm
----------------------------

vagrant basebox build buddycloud
vagrant basebox export buddycloud
vagrant up
vagrant ssh

Work In Progress
----------------

This is still a work in progress and does not yet provide a fully functional
virtual machine.
